# - Try to find ZMQ
# Once done this will define
#
#  ZeroMQ_FOUND - system has ZMQ
#  ZeroMQ_INCLUDE_DIRS - the ZMQ include directory
#  ZeroMQ_LIBRARIES - Link these to use ZMQ
#  ZeroMQ_DEFINITIONS - Compiler switches required for using ZMQ
